net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component

Interface ListModelComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component, Iterable<Component>, LocaleContextSource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComboBox, ListComponent, RichList, SearchableComboBox

    public interface ListModelComponent
extends Component
    Defines an interface for components which have a data model based on ListModel.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)

      • getCellRenderer

        ListCellRenderer getCellRenderer()
        Get the cell renderer used to render values for the component. An appropriate default renderer must be provided that should display the result of the toString() method on the value.
        Returns:
        ListCellRenderer.

      • getModel

        ListModel getModel()
        Get the data model. Changes can be made to the model and the medium will update accordingly assuming the model implementation fires appropriate events.
        Returns:
        ListModel.

      • getModelElementAt

        Object getModelElementAt(String elementId,
                       int elementIndex)
        Get a value from the model.
        Parameters:
        elementId - The element ID.
        elementIndex - The suggested element index which may have the given ID, if the ID does not match this parameter is ignored.
        Returns:
        Object.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the index or element ID does not exist in the model.

      • getSelectionModel

        ListSelectionModel getSelectionModel()
        Get the selection model. Methods are allowed to be called on this object, the medium will update accordingly.

        ListSelectionModel.
